There are effective ways to treat lung cancer, but its mortality rate is so high because so many patients are "n't" diagnosed until their disease is in an advanced stage, Connery said.
Doctors said most lung cancer patients can continue to work throughout treatment, but need flexibility to take it easy on days they are not feeling well.
